OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FA woman living next to a Staffordshire
OL,8,Fghost village after HS2 purchased
OL,9,Fhomes for the now-scrapped northern
OL,10,Fleg of the route, says it's been left
OL,11,Fin a state that's "shameful and a
OL,12,Fnational scandal".
OL,14,FWhitmore was directly on the path of
OL,15,FHS2's proposed route from Birmingham
OL,16,Fto Manchester, prompting several
OL,17,Fhomeowners to sell their properties to
OL,18,Fthe company.
OL,20,FHS2 says it acquired 41 properties in
OL,21,Fthe village.
