OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FThe in October has left several homes,
OL,8,Feach worth up to a million pounds,
OL,9,Fremaining empty with their gates
OL,10,Fchained up and their surroundings
OL,11,Fmonitored by 24/7 CCTV.
OL,13,FDeborah Mallender, from neighbouring
OL,14,Fvillage Madeley, says the number of
OL,15,Fhouses still vacant by the rail
OL,16,Fproject is yet another example of its
OL,17,Fmismanagement.
