OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,F"It's shameful. It's a scandal. It's a
OL,8,Fnational scandal. When people are
OL,9,Fcrying out for money like councils,
OL,10,Fthe NHS, education - all these people
OL,11,Fare crying out for extra cash and here
OL,12,Fwe have public money, standing,
OL,13,Frotting away."
OL,15,FHS2 Ltd says some of the 41 properties
OL,16,Fin Whitmore are now being rented back
OL,17,Fto people on short-term contracts.
OL,19,FOthers have been left vacant for
OL,20,Fyears, leading to fears that they've
OL,21,Fbeen damaged by damp, mould and pests.
