OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FDeborah Mallender told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral: "These houses should have all
OL,9,Fbeen put on the market by now and we
OL,10,Fshould be having normal families
OL,11,Flooking at these houses, living in
OL,12,Fthese houses. HS2 have left this area
OL,13,Fin the state of a dog's breakfast."
OL,15,FThe decision to scrap the Birmingham
OL,16,Fto Manchester leg was made by the
OL,17,Fgovernment back in October at the
OL,18,FConservative Party Conference, in
OL,19,FManchester.
