OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak lamented
OL,8,Fthe project's spiralling costs and
OL,9,Ffrequent delays.
OL,11,FDespite that, there currently remains
OL,12,Flots of HS2 activity across northern
OL,13,FStaffordshire which has prevented some
OL,14,Fresidents from leaving.
OL,16,FOne homeowner, who wasn't able to sell
OL,17,Fhis house to HS2 Ltd, told ITV News
OL,18,FCentral he had been unable to sell his
OL,19,Fproperty on the market because buyers
OL,20,Fwere uncertain about whether the rail
OL,21,Fproject would be started in future.
