OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FAlastair Frew is a partner at Lodders
OL,8,FSolicitors, who specialise in land and
OL,9,Fproperty. He says the ongoing
OL,10,Fassociation between HS2 and Whitmore
OL,11,Fmeans many residents may become
OL,12,Ftrapped due to their inability to sell.
