OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FHe said: "The poor people of Whitmore
OL,8,Fare in a bit of a predicament at the
OL,9,Fmoment. If you were buying a house in
OL,10,Fa village where there was a chance
OL,11,Fthat this big project might be
OL,12,Fresurrected you'd probably think 'I'll
OL,13,Flook at a different village' and
OL,14,Fthat's the awful shame for those poor
OL,15,Fpeople who live there."
OL,17,FBut for others, the scrapping of the
OL,18,Fleg to Manchester represents a chance
OL,19,Fto seize back what was theirs.
