OL,3,C'A national scandal': The
OL,4,CStaffordshire ghost village made empty
OL,5,Cby HS2
OL,7,FFarmer Edward Cavenagh-Mainwaring sold
OL,8,Fhis land to HS2 back in September
OL,9,Fafter 10 years of stressful
OL,10,Fnegotiation.
OL,12,FThe following month, the government
OL,13,Fcancelled the route. He admits he
OL,14,Fwould buy back his fields, but only at
OL,15,Fthe right price.
OL,17,FHe said: "I have very strong
OL,18,Fattachments to the land that are hard
OL,19,Fto describe and probably hard for
OL,20,Fother people to comprehend.
