OL,7,F"I hope that we are offered this land
OL,8,Fback and we're in a position to
OL,9,Frepurchase it provided the land price
OL,10,Freflects the price that they took it
OL,11,Ffrom us at."
OL,13,FThe government says it is still
OL,14,Fdeveloping a programme for selling
OL,15,Fproperty no longer needed by HS2 - one
OL,16,Fwhich fully engages with the community.
